<div id='about-me'></div>
<section class="about">
  <h2 class='heading-secondary heading-secondary--color-primary u-mb-m'>About me</h2>

  <div class="about__content u-mb-l">
    <p>Hi, I’m Kenta, a Front-End Developer based in Yokohama, Japan. With a background blending both Filipino and Japanese heritage, I am fluent in Tagalog, English, and Japanese (JLPT N2).</p>
    <p>My expertise lies in JavaScript, where I focus on building scalable, user-focused websites and applications that deliver seamless experiences. I emphasize best practices, clean, maintainable code, and accessibility to ensure optimal outcomes for both users and developers.</p>
    <p>Driven by curiosity and a passion for growth, I welcome new challenges as opportunities to refine my skills and continuously improve my craft.</p>
    <p>In my free time, you’ll find me at the skatepark or at the gym, staying active and inspired. 🛹🏋🏻</p>
  </div>

  <h3 class='heading-tertiary heading-tertiary--color-tertiary u-mb-m'>MY SKILLS</h3>

  <div class='about__skills'>
    <ul class='about__skills-list'>
      <% data.tech_stack.each do |tech_name, tech_info| %>
        <li class='about__skills-list__item'>
          <p><%= tech_name %></p>
          <img src="<%= tech_info['src'] %>" alt="<%= tech_info['alt'] %>">
        </li>
      <% end %>
    </ul>
  </div>
</section>
